badge and it’s Usage

Badges can be used as part of any component and are available in below formats:

badge

Package Name
fifthtry.github.io/bling/badge
To use these badges on your web package, add below lines into FPM.ftd file:
-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/bling
-- fpm.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/bling/badge

-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/bling
-- fpm.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/bling/badge
Once you add above lines into your web package, add badge into your .ftd files:

All badge examples:

Light
Dark
Primary
Secondary
Info
Warning
Success
Danger
